1. Vožnja *autobusom* je najjeftiniji način putovanja. (Traveling *by bus* is the cheapest way to travel.)
2. Juče sam otišao u *vožnju* biciklom sa prijateljima. (Yesterday, I went for a *bike ride* with friends.)
3. Nisam u mogućnosti da te odvezem, moraš sama organizovati svoju *vožnju*. (I am not able to drive you, you have to organize your own *ride*.)
4. Vozači treba da obrate pažnju na uslove puta tokom *vožnje*. (Drivers should pay attention to the road conditions during *driving*.)
5. Da li si spremna za *vožnju* rolera? (Are you ready for *roller skating*?)
6. Ne mogu da se usredsredim tokom *vožnje* ako mi neko stalno zvoni na telefon. (I can't concentrate during *driving* if someone keeps calling me on the phone.)
7. Posle *vožnje* u krug, vozač je konačno pronašao put do našeg odredišta. (After driving in circles, the driver finally found the way to our destination.) 
8. Deca se uvek raduju *vožnji* rolera u parku. (Children always enjoy *roller skating* in the park.)
9. Naši planovi za vikend uključuju *vožnju* kanuom niz reku. (Our weekend plans include *canoeing* down the river.)
10. Nezgoda se desila tokom *vožnje* automobila kroz gužvu u gradu. (The accident happened during *driving* the car through the city traffic jam.)